{"tid":828012,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"覺唔覺得香港嘅請飲文化好撚乞衣？","createTime":"2018-09-19T11:03:45.000Z","updateTime":"2018-09-19T12:26:30.000Z","uid":65024,"like":36,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"0f71a8e3e439dad4a80c51f6765e072d11888559","tid":828012,"uid":65024,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-19T11:03:45.000Z","msg":"你結婚關我撚事？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n你個仔一百日大關我撚事？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n你老母八十歲關我撚事？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n唉都算，收你張帖唔黎都要畀禮？你唔好去搶？你面皮厚到好意思收？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我真係試過收到個親戚張帖，連我個名都寫錯，我轉個頭掉落垃圾筒當無收過<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n再講，咩叫請飲？我肯用我寶貴嘅時間出席已經非常俾面你，仲要收禮咪即係我地全部人請返你擺酒？呢D行為同乞錢有咩分別？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d5dd1844a466af12299e2310a92b6f536d12acbf","tid":828012,"uid":60831,"like":6,"dislike":1,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-19T11:06:29.000Z","msg":"請飲 = 自己出錢請對新人飲"},{"pid":"6cfc42fe52f892afbf72243c033680dca1c652e8","tid":828012,"uid":65024,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d5dd1844a466af12299e2310a92b6f536d12acbf","tid":828012,"uid":60831,"like":6,"dislike":1,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-19T11:06:29.000Z","msg":"請飲 = 自己出錢請對新人飲"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-19T11:08:13.000Z","msg":"畀著我真係做唔出<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"05cc713820fd6e595596c0e46c270f7d70987103","tid":828012,"uid":198400,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-19T11:12:58.000Z","msg":"支那文化<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e8076d0fb6daa15e0f83fc36b6d15ac367a9ffd0","tid":828012,"uid":171506,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-19T11:27:42.000Z","msg":"結婚擺酒一向戇居"},{"pid":"0aa28ed